Class Material

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ithaca.iclibrary.Material

  • public class Material
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to represent books/items in the library. Member variables are derived from library XML response. Created by Kelly on 3/29/2016.

                java.lang.String locationName,
                int mfhdCount,
                int itemCount,
                int itemStatusCode,
                java.lang.String isbn)
        Parameters:
        bibId: - String, internal id number from library
        bibText1: - String, primary book descriptor
        bibText2: - String, secondary book descriptor
        bibText3: - String, tertiary book descriptor
        callNumber: - String, call number for location in library
        locationName: - String, name of general location in library
        mfhdCount: - int, MFHD record
        itemCount: - int, number of item available
        itemStatusCode: - int, 1 = available, 0 = checked out, -1 = n/a
        isbn: - String isbn
